[HR]

[SIZE=4][B]Quick start[/B][/SIZE]

[LIST=1]
[*]Download [B]ItemMagnet-1.2.1.jar[/B] and place it in [CODE]plugins/[/CODE]
[*]Restart your Paper server
[*][CODE]/itemmagnet give YourName fragment 500[/CODE]
[*]Hold the magnet; fuel with redstone dust (sneak + right-click)
[*]Drop items nearby — they pull with visible motion
[/LIST]

Optional: [CODE]/itemmagnet config[/CODE] to open the in-game editor.

[HR]

[SIZE=4][B]Migrating from the old 2021 build[/B][/SIZE]

Treat this as a [B]fresh install[/B]:

[LIST]
[*]Config format, commands, and permissions have changed
[*]Review [CODE]plugins/ItemMagnet/config.yml[/CODE] on first run or use [CODE]/itemmagnet config[/CODE]
[*]Old magnet items in player inventories may need to be re-given
[*]Integrations (Lands, WorldGuard, etc.) are optional but recommended for SMPs
[/LIST]

Full command and permission reference is in the resource [B]Documentation[/B] tab and on the website.

[HR]

[SIZE=4][B]v1.2.1 changelog highlights[/B][/SIZE]

[LIST]
[*]Config GUI tier renaming (chat input from tier editor)
[*]Live [CODE]{radius}[/CODE] and [CODE]{base_radius}[/CODE] lore placeholders
[*]Per-fuel recharge sounds and improved fuel transfer (either hand)
[*][CODE]/itemmagnet giveall[/CODE] and [CODE]/itemmagnet unlockall[/CODE]
[*]AFK [CODE]notify-once[/CODE], permission-filtered help, reload restart warnings
[/LIST]

